#

Vegetarian Cheese Curry

30 min
$10
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Indian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy cheese curry that's easy to make and packed with flavor!

Ingredients

  • paneer (indian cheese): 200 grams
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • tomato: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • curry powder: 1 tablespoon
  • turmeric powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro: for garnish
